        "title": "Finally! Someone who gets Agile and DevOps — to the point🤖",
        "excerpt":"For 25 years we’ve been preaching the basic principles of Agile and DevOps to teams, colleagues and clients. Now, as Agentic AI matures to truly spec-drive development  — a whole new breed of code contributors are entering the stage. And they get EXACTLY what it’s about. What Could Possibly Go Wrong?   The event is free to participate - SEATS ARE LIMITED TO 40!   Venue        Venue    The Workbar         Matrikel 1, Gammel Strand 26, Copenhagen                   Website                 Map           Program   For 25 years we’ve been preaching the basic principles of Agile and DevOps to teams, colleagues and clients. Both Agile and DevOps have been declared DEAD many times. But now it’s apparently un-dead, as Agentic AI matures by the hour — a whole new breed of code contributors are entering the stage.   And they get EXACTLY what it’s about: Agentic AI may just be the the best Agile and most DevOpsy team mates one could dream of.   What could possibly go wrong now?   You are hereby invited to a short intro (roughly 30 mins, expect slightly provocative and opinionated content — something that old men are still way better at than AI) followed by a facilitated lean coffee discussion on an apocaloptimistic perspective on:   “What the heck is going on in Agile and DevOps Right Now”   The venue is a bar 🍻 - so do not expect anything other than lively discussions with peers.   We’re kicked out of the Workbar at 19:00 by the latest, but if the sentiment is right we may continue on to somewhere else and grab a bite after.      Cheers!   facilitators                                                                                                Klaus Bucka-Lassen &amp; Lars Kruse        25 years of Agile and DevOps expertise                                                                                                           Finally someone gets Agile and DevOps to the point                                                                                   Klaus Bucka-Lassen: An agile advisor and consultant with 25+ years experience with helping organizations streamline their agile processes.   Lars Kruse: A Continuous Delivery and DevOps evangelist and consultant with 25+ years experience with helping organizations streamline their SDLC processes.  ","categories": [],
