        "title": "AI-Driven Infrastructure Operations: Scaling Smarter on NVIDIA Hardware",
        "excerpt":"AI is reshaping how we operate infrastructure, especially on NVIDIA hardware. This talk will explore how GPUs revolutionized AI, the evolution of AI infrastructure, and how efficient compute practices are transforming operations. We’ll discuss key tools, techniques, and lessons learned from managing AI workloads at scale.  ","categories": [],
